function Card({ card, onConfirmCard }) {
    return ( <
        div className = "card__elements"
        id = { `id${card._id}` } >
        <
        button className = "card__delete"
        onClick = { onConfirmCard } > < /button> <
        img src = { card.link }
        className = "card__photo"
        alt = "" / >
        <
        div className = "card__text" >
        <
        h2 className = "card__tittle" > { card.name } < /h2> <
        div className = "card__column" >
        <
        button type = "button"
        className = "card__like" > < /button> <
        span className = "card__like-count" > { card.likes.length ? card.likes.length : 0 } <
        /span> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    )
}
export default Card
